title: Azure DevOps to GitHub - The 10 Missing Bits
eventShortDescription:
September .NET User Group: Azure DevOps to GitHub - The 10 Missing Bits

GitHub is the best engineering platform for developers, and has really matured in recent years. Still, we hear developers say "I can't believe that I can't do this on GitHub, it's easy on Azure DevOps 🔥".

In this talk, Matt Wicks will give you the top 10 things you need to know to turn those frowns upside down and make development great again.
